Package: prism
Type: Pacakge
Title: Probe Re-Identification and Sequence Mapping
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Dunning", 
                  email = "m.dunning@imperial.ac.uk", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8853-9435")
Description: Re-annotates legacy microarray datasets using current genome 
    builds and gene annotations. Maps probe sequences to modern reference 
    genomes, updates gene annotations from Ensembl, identifies problematic 
    probes, and reprocesses expression matrices. Enables researchers to 
    extract new insights from thousands of legacy datasets in repositories 
    like GEO.
